    "Within this category, 'Intellectual Property (IP) and Knowledge Creation' was acknowledged by 15.4% of the experts, whereas the Evolution of Traditional Models' was highlighted by 12.8%.",
    "These insights underline the role of DeSci in fostering innovation and the evolution of traditional research paradigms.",
    "The 'Ethical and Philosophical Aspects' category synthesizes responses related to the ethical and philosophical challenges and principles of DeSci mentioned by 25.6% of experts.",
